OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FResidents of the UK's smallest county
OL,8,Fare campaigning to bring a giant
OL,9,Ffossil back to the area, despite the
OL,10,Fcouncil saying it would cost too much
OL,11,Fto maintain.
OL,13,FThe 180 million year old Ichthyosaur
OL,14,Fwas found at Rutland Water Nature
OL,15,FReserve during maintenance work in
OL,16,F2021.
OL,18,FThe ancient marine reptile, measuring
OL,19,Fmore than 10 metres long, is the
OL,20,Flargest ever discovered in Britain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FIt's currently owned by Anglian Water,
OL,8,Fbut Rutland County Council had been
OL,9,Fplanning to bring it back to the area
OL,10,Fand display it at the Rutland County
OL,11,FMuseum in Oakham as part of a #6m
OL,12,Fproject.
OL,14,FHowever, the council has said it can
OL,15,Fno longer afford this and has pulled
OL,16,Fthe plug on the plans.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FLaurence Fenelon is a local campaigner
OL,8,Fbacking the fight to save the fossil.
OL,9,FHe told ITV News Central: "It would
OL,10,Fbring enormous economic benefits, we
OL,11,Fthink, in terms of attracting more
OL,12,Ftourists.
OL,14,F"Rutland is a lovely county and it
OL,15,Fneeds more tourists to help the
OL,16,Feconomy. It would put our museum on
OL,17,Fthe map for the long term."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FAnglian Water told ITV News it would
OL,8,Fcontinue to preserve the fossil, but
OL,9,Fthat it was disappointed at the county
OL,10,Fcouncil's decision as they had agreed
OL,11,Fto hand over the Jurassic giant for
OL,12,Ffree.
OL,14,FA spokesperson added: "Through our
OL,15,Fdiscussions with the council we'd made
OL,16,Fsignificant progress towards an
OL,17,Fagreement to transfer the Sea Dragon
OL,18,Fat no cost to the council for its
OL,19,Facquisition."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FBut the county council said it's the
OL,8,Fcost of housing and maintaining the
OL,9,Ffossil in the museum which is
OL,10,Funaffordable.
OL,12,FCllr Andrew Johnson, deputy leader of
OL,13,Fthe council, said: "The cost of
OL,14,Fconserving it we currently estimate is
OL,15,Fover one million pounds and that's
OL,16,Fclimbing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,F"We think because of the strengthening
OL,8,Fof the foundations and differences in
OL,9,Fthe walls and the height of ceiling,
OL,10,Fthat would add a further approximate
OL,11,F#1million to the bill.
OL,13,F"So we're looking closer to #2
OL,14,Fmillion."
OL,16,FDespite this, many people in Oakham
OL,17,Fbelieve the fossil needs to be kept in
OL,18,Fthe town it was discovered.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1780308639
OL,3,CCampaign to bring Britain's largest
OL,4,C'Sea Dragon' back to UK's smallest
OL,5,Ccounty
OL,7,FA petition was launched by the Friends
OL,8,Fof Rutland County Museum and Oakham
OL,9,FCastle and has now received 2,000
OL,10,Fsignatures, meaning the council is
OL,11,Frequired to hold a full debate on the
OL,12,Fmatter.
OL,14,FIf the council doesn't change its mind
OL,15,Fon the decision, Anglian Water say it
OL,16,Fwill tell the story of the Sea Dragon
OL,17,Fat the Anglian Water Bird Watching
OL,18,FCentre at Rutland Water Nature Reserve.
OL,20,FHowever, the fossil itself will be
OL,21,Fstored at a secure location elsewhere.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
